{"tid":218100,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[無人開?] 夏目友人帳第六季03 雙偶","createTime":"2017-04-26T09:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T10:29:47.000Z","uid":42011,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6b38e79d8aced4abc7aa74e27f79c684182198","tid":218100,"uid":42011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lqg9knwb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flqg9knwb&h=74b139f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夏目友人帳》劇情主要描述夏目是一位具有靈異體質的高中生,他能看見別人看不到的鬼怪,在他得到祖母的遺物「友人帳」之後,不論白天或晚上,開始有各式各樣的妖怪來找他,讓夏目深受其擾,但是在夏目在得知事情原委之後,決心要將友人帳上的名字, 一一還給被祖母擊敗的妖怪。而妖怪貓咪老師則自願保護夏目和友人帳,和夏目共同踏上妖怪之旅。<br />\nbilibili:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bangumi.bilibili.com/anime/5977/play#103966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbangumi.bilibili.com%2Fanime%2F5977%2Fplay%23103966&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=371abd9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bangumi.bilibili.com/anime/5977/play#103966</a><br />\nviutv<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/46031/%E5%A4%8F%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B3%20%E9%99%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F46031%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B8%25B3%2520%25E9%2599%25B8&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=073497c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/46031/%E5%A4%8F%E7%9B%AE%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B3%20%E9%99%B8</a>"},{"pid":"8398cddde36041a34cfa8f2fdea966b0adb68661","tid":218100,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要冇講原故咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4286c704b71ed23a5f976a35afd17ee7c6640544","tid":218100,"uid":42011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:39:32.000Z","